data.text:
About Us

Founded in 1972 by Prosper native Dan Christie, Collin County Land Company is one of the oldest real estate firms in North Texas, selling properties in Collin, Grayson, Denton, Fannin, Hunt and Cooke Counties.Â Whether you are buying or selling a home, homesite, raw land for personal use, investment or development or a commercial property, we offer years of experience, knowledge of the market and professional service.Â We also provide leasing and management services for residential and commercial properties.

Thanks for visiting our website.Â We look forward to the opportunity to work with you.
